But, what about his hand?

120
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:23,400
His finger is broken.

121
00:09:23,730 --> 00:09:25,500
I really can't discuss
the case with you.

122
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:27,519
It looks like a defensive wound

123
