taking me seriously?

158
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:01,609
We are taking you and this
case extremely seriously.

159
00:11:01,610 --> 00:11:04,099
That is why I am going to
pass this on to DI Winstanley,

160
00:11:04,100 --> 00:11:05,630
