He hasn't been in touch
for months, right?

192
00:13:40,730 --> 00:13:42,590
Since just after the fire?

193
00:13:43,770 --> 00:13:45,170
Do you know what
the weird thing is?

194
00:13:48,350 --> 00:13:50,270
Before I knew where
he was all the time

195
