226
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,280
I've got a good memory.

227
00:16:03,493 --> 00:16:04,592
No.

228
00:16:04,593 --> 00:16:06,120
Oliver Gough may be the killer.

229
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:08,040
